Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't touched alcohol\Nsince then, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start over again\Nas long as you don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't drink when I see you\Nonce a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a respectable counselor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have\Nthe time to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my first big case\Nsince becoming a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Big case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you think of this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein, using physiognomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of man do you think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Physiognomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you mistaking me\Nfor a fortune-teller or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what you're known for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that you can tell a person's\Npersonality just by looking at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the result of many years\Nof interviewing clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then using the results\Nof those interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,see if this guy is a con man or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A con man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have\Nthe face of a con man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the type that would\Nimmediately expose himself if he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the possibility that\Nhe'd commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all. People with faces like this\Nwould never kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your physiognomy\Nis strangely convincing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,when said so straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of interviews!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So did something happen\Nto this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans Georg Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you know who he is,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You mean the wealthy...\NVampire of Bavaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:02:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That tycoon is my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in the photograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward Fahren, was pretending\Nto be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave himself away, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Schuwald\Ncompletely believed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He cleverly deceived him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I had trouble figuring out\Nthat he was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But a mystery still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know enough\Nabout Schuwald's son
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Schuwald believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should ask him that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's actually\Nalready killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're old friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me see\NEdmund Fahren's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting has been analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is definitely his writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to show\Noutsiders like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Neumann and Lotte Frank,\Nthe ones who discovered the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They worked at the same\Npart-time job as Fahren, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm always shorthanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a break\Nsince I took over your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slowpoke Martin" has\Nbecome a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer my superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly don't know\Nhow much trouble we had back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We took all that time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and almost arrested\Nthat multiple homicide offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were drunk\Nand shot him to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All that trouble\Nto clean up afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time to deal\Nwith a simple suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to check out the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've preserved it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. It's not a crime, so\Npermission has already been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be clearing out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the possessions of\Nthe deceased today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When did "Slowpoke Martin"\Nbecome so efficient?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A broker will be coming to\Ntake everything away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. It'll just be 2 or 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He hung the rope from this pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote his suicide note\Nat this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A paper he was writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Birth of Tragedy, Process and\NReality, World Views on Psychology...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A typical\Nphilosophy student's bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These were the materials\Nhe used to write this paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Caesar's {\i1}Gallic Wars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is only this book\Nunrelated to the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Spanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, is this Latin?\NI can't read this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a clean book,\Nbut it's only underlined here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 204... Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring more cardboard boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the books in the boxes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do with this desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about\Nthe room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not with the police.\NI'm a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever you are,\Nyou're being a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to turn in a paper tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to concentrate\Nbecause of all the trouble next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.\NThen just one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were these two close to Fahren?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NI've never seen them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy next door...didn't seem like\Nhe had many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you translate\Nthis underlined part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be your fault if I fail my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... "I no longer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"...can continue"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,," ...to deceive."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"I no longer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"...can continue"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"...to deceive."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like this place as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if I remember correctly,\Nyou're...Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up here. You can see\Nthe view better from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. It's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights of the houses go on\Nat about this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Families are coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts to smell like\Ndinnertime everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I long for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You long for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've never had dinner with\Nmy family ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your family like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Did I ask\Nsomething offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually taken in\Nby foster parents when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything!\NThis is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer\Ncontinue to deceive."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Fahren's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a translation\Nof that line from this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit depressing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange. I can talk to you\Nabout anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rich father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crying for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. We've got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I take care of Schuwald\Nand I can't help but worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been eating much\Nsince Fahren's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, he's going to die next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl... Why don't you tell him that\Nyou're his real son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see\Nwhat kind of person he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told him the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd think that I was someone\Nwho was after his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald is that kind of person.\NEverything is about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't understand my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true father is suffering\Nin the depths of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer continue to deceive."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The note that Fahren left\Nwasn't a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This Latin book was in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just translating\Nthis underlined part in Gallic Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like this is a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have conclusive proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my intuition\Nfrom many years as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Mr. Schuwald?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem very energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NIt's not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he didn't commit suicide,\Nyour life may be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I already informed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither his birthplace\Nnor his background
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,has anything to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fahren was indeed a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't the kind of person\Nwho would con people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But he tried to trick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The master is tired.\NPlease leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to end the investigation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not saying that because\Nthis is my first high-profile job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an even bigger evil\Nin the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things we can never redo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand...very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm continuing the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A treaty of children's rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,an international standard to protect\Nthe civil liberties of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I'm working on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But volunteering to take care of\Nthe children at this facility
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is unrelated to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...could you tell us more about\Nwhat you said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald went bankrupt\Nthree times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Each of those three times,\Nhe'd disappear temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he'd reappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,he worked tirelessly\Nto regain his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me about that\Nwhen I did my Friday reading job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask him where he went\Nwhen he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We should take him there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a place\Nthat makes him feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how you look at the houses\Nfrom the roof of the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuntz, it looks like\Nthe bathroom sink is clogged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, what's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Open up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nwith the master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The master can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!\NKidnappers, kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!\NOur plan was a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that\Nyou're not Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want information on Fahren,\Nthe boy who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He came here, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fahren...which one was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Two groups came claiming to be\NSchuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the blond one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it the black-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Black-haired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-haired one came with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he'd bring a girl\Nto a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Black hair...and a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...said that he was Schuwald's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.\NIt should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you taken me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Owenberg Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought it would cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the autumn leaves\Nof the woods beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the wrens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear the chirping of the wrens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has become...\Nan industrial area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chirping so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Many apples have fallen in the grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The autumn leaves look like\Nthey're on fire in the afternoon sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being reflected like a mirror\Non the calm surface of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that\Nsuch a sight exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that two groups came here.\NThe black-haired boy brought a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Fahren didn't come by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The blond came with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fahren kid you speak of\Ncouldn't speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy he called his friend\Ntold me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have believed him if he said\Nthat he was Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
